<h4 id="disable-fast-startup">disable fast startup</h4>

<p>control panel–&gt; power options–&gt;choose what buttons do–&gt; change
unavilable settings–&gt; turn off fast boot–&gt; save changes</p>

<h4 id="disable-secure-boot">disable secure boot?</h4>
<p>F2
<a href="https://itsfoss.com/disable-secure-boot-in-acer/">set password in bios to change secure boot</a>
now disable boot</p>

